rows.label: qst201316_msg0004
rows.name:
You seem to be Luxurian...
How did you end up here?

rows.label: qst201316_msg0005
rows.name:
Um, I... I just woke up here, I
don't know how it happened...

rows.label: qst201316_msg0006
rows.name:
I was scared, and I tried
to make a run for it, but
then that monster, it...

rows.label: qst201316_msg0008
rows.name:
I always thought that spiriting away
stuff was just nonsense, but it's
starting to sound more likely...

rows.label: qst201316_msg0009
rows.name: It's too early to say for sure.

rows.label: qst201316_msg0010
rows.name:
For the moment, let's just
head back to Fons Maim and
report in to Dianna.

rows.label: qst201316_msg0012
rows.name:
It doesn't seem likely, but there's
always a chance this is one of
the kids she's looking for.
